Package gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GUI
    GUI base on Swing JtextArea.
    ModificationFilter
    This class filters input in TextArea.
    ReplayButton
    ReplayButton implements the behavior of the replayButton (enable/disable)
    SelectionListener
    SelectionListener is to listen on changes on the selection in the JTextArea, to ensure synchronization between selection in JTextArea and the selection object in the edition engine.
    StartButton
    StartButton implements the behavior of the start button (enable/disable).
    StopButton
    StopButton implements the behavior of the stop button (enable/disable).
    TextAreaCustom
    TextAreaCustom inherits of the swing JtextArea to implement the copy, paste and cut actions.
